> >>Replace the dependency on NFSD_V3 with a "select NFSD_V3".  This  
> >>makes
> >>NFSD_V4 look and work just like NFS_V3, while ensuring that  
> >>NFSD_V3 is
> >>enabled if NFSD_V4 is.
